     "status" -> "None", "summary" -> 
    "NambuCoefficients[expr, {a1, ..., an}] gets a vector or matrix of \
coefficients in a linear combination or linear combinations of the \
annihilation and creation operators of Dirac fermion modes {a1, ..., an}. \
NambuCoefficients[expr, {c1, c2, ..., c 2 n}] returns a vector or matrix of \
coefficients in a linear combination or linear combinations of Majorana \
fermion operators {c1, c2, ..., c 2 n}, and transforms it to a vector or \
matrix of coefficients in the equivalent linear combination(s) of the \
Majorana operators corresponding to the Dirac fermion modes.", 
